  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAttachment
    The Interface IAttachment provides an abstraction of an attachment in the platform
    IAttachmentProcessor
    The IAttachmentProcessor interfaces allows for the platform to interact with the application to initiate attachment download.

    IAttachmentService provides the interface for an application to interact with the platform to process attachments.
